data.description: Sellers Offering $10,000 Credit towards interest rate buy down. Come view this beautifully taken care of, spacious home at a competitive price. This home offers 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a separate office and a loft as well as a huge great room. Ideal for extended family living with a full bedroom/bath and separate office on the main level as well as three more bedrooms and an oversized loft on the upper level. The kitchen great room combo sports a fireplace and opens to a cozy back yard which has plenty of space for whatever you need. NO HOA! Family friendly neighborhood, close to schools, and shopping.
